## Description {#details}

A specialized priority queue for WeigthedLeaves.

It automatically folds constants and allows removal of non-top elements while maintaining the priority order.

Definition at line 1824 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/target/lib/target/hexagon/hexagoniseldagtodag-cpp">HexagonISelDAGToDAG.cpp</a>.
